e in network\nrobustness and/or the emergence of more specialised functional modules.\nAdditionally, we find stress induces tighter co-regulation of non-coding RNAs,\ndecreased functional importance of splicing factors, as well as changes in the\ncentrality of genes involved in chromatin organization, cytoskeleton\norganization, cell division, and protein turnover.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Mar 2013 16:25:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-03-21"}
