 be understood in terms of pressure\ntuning of electron correlations, illustrating the unconventional nature of\nsuperconductivity in these hydrocarbon superconductors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Mar 2013 07:39:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Apr 2013 22:56:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-04-15"}
